  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Recruitment Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams for new requirements and staffing needs.</p></li><li><p>Maintain candidate and stakeholder relations, providing timely updates.</p></li><li><p>Schedule and coordinate interviews, feedback, onboarding, and background checks.</p></li><li><p>Manage end-to-end recruitment activities and document management.</p></li><li><p>Track candidate pipelines, open roles, and recruitment progress.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with local and global teams to ensure smooth hiring processes.</p></li><li><p>Maintain organized records of candidate feedback and recruitment data.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Skills & Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Excellent written and verbal communication skills.</p></li><li><p>Strong interpersonal skills and customer service orientation.</p></li><li><p>High attention to detail and strong organizational ability.</p></li><li><p>Ability to adapt quickly and learn new processes.</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, PowerPoint).</p></li><li><p>Experience with HR systems and data tracking is a plus.</p></li><li><p>Ability to maintain confidentiality and produce high-quality work.<br /><br />This position is open to all who are fulfilling aforesaid requirements</p></li></ul><p><strong></strong></p>",
